Monsters.Name: Corruption
Monsters.Comments:
Note: An end-game standard ecounter. Should wipe the party if they hit it during their Jail dungeon run. It must be dodged to get the treasures.

No-auto:
- It gives reduced gold just in case you kill it.
  It would make you kinda too rich to farm these otherwise I think.
  I did auto's value divided by 10.
- Less EXP.
- More JP.
